Room.Name: Golden Dolphin Way
Room.ShortDescription: You are walking along Golden Dolphin Way, behind the Archery Range.
Room.LongDescription: On the north side of the road, you can see the Dentra Central Archery Range, where many archers and civilians alike go to practice their bow and arrow skills either for the hunt or just self-defense. As with most archery ranges, elves are always present, trying to prove that they're better than anyone else.
